&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;BankThink Get customers to help you protect their data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to a Verizon study of data breaches, hackers are breaking in faster and it&amp;rsquo;s taking longer for banks to find them. In 2015, 84% of hacks were &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.americanbanker.com/opinion/get-customers-to-help-you-protect-their-data&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.americanbanker.com/opinion/get-customers-to-help-you-protect-their-data&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

