&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;sup&gt;28&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;frasl;&lt;sub&gt;03&lt;/sub&gt;-2017 07:00:31: Gemalto releases findings of 2016 Breach Level Index&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;59% of all data breaches. In addition, 52% of the data breaches in 2016 did &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://hopey.netfonds.no/release.php?id=20170328.GlobeNewswire.HUG2090791&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://hopey.netfonds.no/release.php?id=20170328.GlobeNewswire.HUG2090791&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches continue to rise in the connected age&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gemalto&amp;rsquo;s Breach Level Index has revealed that 1,792 data breaches led to almost 1.4 billion data records being compromised worldwide during 2016 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-age.com/data-breaches-continue-rise-connected-age-123465347/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-age.com/data-breaches-continue-rise-connected-age-123465347/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Laptops with personal data of 3.7 million Hong Kong voters stolen&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hong Kong has become the latest victim in data theft in what could possibly count as one of the city&amp;rsquo;s most significant data breaches if information is &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cnet.com/news/laptops-with-personal-data-of-3-7-million-hong-kong-voters-stolen/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.cnet.com/news/laptops-with-personal-data-of-3-7-million-hong-kong-voters-stolen/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;55M data records compromised in the UK last year, up 575% on 2015&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The UK was behind only US in the number of data breaches it suffered last year, according to research by Gemalto. Of the 1,792 data breaches &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-age.com/55m-data-records-compromised-uk-last-year-575-2015-123465356/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-age.com/55m-data-records-compromised-uk-last-year-575-2015-123465356/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cloud Distribution Advances Security Portfolio with Endpoint Protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RealWire (press release) (blog) &amp;hellip; only platform to unify next-generation antivirus (AV), endpoint detection and response (EDR) and managed hunting &amp;ndash; all delivered through the cloud &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://blogit.realwire.com/Cloud-Distribution-Advances-Security-Portfolio-with-Endpoint-Protection&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://blogit.realwire.com/Cloud-Distribution-Advances-Security-Portfolio-with-Endpoint-Protection&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;New hacks, new defenses: Latest tips to protect against data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protecting yourself from hackers and data breaches requires constant vigilance. Last year&amp;rsquo;s tips don&amp;rsquo;t necessarily hold up to this year&amp;rsquo;s attacks.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cbsnews.com/news/online-security-tips-how-to-protect-yourself-hackers-data-breaches/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cbsnews.com/news/online-security-tips-how-to-protect-yourself-hackers-data-breaches/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Close to 1.4 billion data records compromised in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identity theft, the authors of the report explained, was the most common type of security incident last year, representing 59% of all data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.welivesecurity.com/2017/03/28/close-1-4-billion-data-records-compromised-2016/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.welivesecurity.com/2017/03/28/close-1-4-billion-data-records-compromised-2016/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Loggly Closes 2016 with 99% Revenue Growth&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SAN FRANCISCO, March 28, 2017 /PRNewswire/ &amp;ndash; Loggly, the leading cloud-based, enterprise-class log management solution provider, announced &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/loggly-closes-2016-99-revenue-120000057.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/loggly-closes-2016-99-revenue-120000057.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;2016 saw huge glut of data breaches, with 1.4bn files compromised&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trying to quantify the number of data breaches in any particular year might seem like a tall order. Not only are SMEs unprepared for the security &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.siliconrepublic.com/enterprise/data-breaches-by-numbers-2016&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.siliconrepublic.com/enterprise/data-breaches-by-numbers-2016&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

