&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Laptops With More than 3.7 Million Hong Kong Voters&amp;rsquo; Data Stolen&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; city&amp;rsquo;s voters personal information that could be compromised after the one of the most significant, if not the biggest ever data breaches in Hong Kong &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.hackread.com/laptops-with-hong-kong-voters-data-stolen/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.hackread.com/laptops-with-hong-kong-voters-data-stolen/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

