&lt;p&gt;Healthcare was hit with 28% of all data breaches, with an 11% year-over-year increase in attacks, and financial services, 12% of data breaches, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/threat-intelligence/14-billion-data-records-exposed-in-2016-breaches/d/d-id/1328501&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/threat-intelligence/14-billion-data-records-exposed-in-2016-breaches/d/d-id/1328501&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

