&lt;p&gt;Gemalto has released the findings of its 2016 Breach Level Index revealing that 1,792 publicly disclosed data breaches led to almost 1.4 billion data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.scmagazineuk.com/gemalto-breach-level-index-14bn-data-records-compromised-in-2016/article/646955/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.scmagazineuk.com/gemalto-breach-level-index-14bn-data-records-compromised-in-2016/article/646955/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Two Daytona State College breaches affect students and staff&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Daytona State College was hit with two data breaches this month that affected both employee and student data. Officials launched an investigation into &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.scmagazine.com/daytona-state-college-hit-with-double-breach-affecting-staff-and-students/article/646957/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.scmagazine.com/daytona-state-college-hit-with-double-breach-affecting-staff-and-students/article/646957/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

